TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select * from ( select Lead(A.seq, 1, 0) OVER (ORDER BY A.agentcode,A.seq desc) as lead_seq, A.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE as EFFECTIVEENDDATE, A.EFFECTIVESTARTDATE as removedate from AIA_CB_BSC_AGENT_LIST_LOG A where agentcode in ( select b.agentcode from (select max(createdate) as createdate from AIA_CB_BSC_AGENT_LIST_LOG)A, (select * from AIA_CB_BSC_AGENT_LIST_LOG) B where a.createdate = b.createdate and b.action='UPDATE') order by A.seq desc) where rownum=1

GROUP.DESCRIPTION: Path for the data when none of the group conditions are satisfied.
GROUP.NAME: DEFAULT1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: select B.YEAR as syb_year, b.quarter as syb_quarter, b.agentcode as syb_agentcode, B.BSC_GRADE as syb_bsc_grade, B.ENTITLEMENTPERCENT as syb_ENTITLEMENTPERCENT, b.createdate as syb_createdate, A.* from AIA_CB_BSC_AGENT A right outer join SYB_INFRACTED_AGENT_LIST B on a.year = b.year and a.quarter = b.quarter and a.agentcode = b.agentcode
